Package magellan.library.utils

Class Regions.MultiDimensionalInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.library.utils.Regions.MultiDimensionalInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Regions.MultiDimensionalInfo>, Regions.RegionInfo
    Enclosing class:
    Regions
    public static class Regions.MultiDimensionalInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements Regions.RegionInfo, java.lang.Comparable<Regions.MultiDimensionalInfo>
    A distance implementation that uses Regions.MultidimensionalDistance. dist is the distance in regions, that has been modified if harbours have been encountered on the path. plus is the number of oceans near the coast or land regions on the path. realDist is the actual length of the path.
    Author:
    stm
